    "description": "<strong>Bravest Chicken</strong> is a precision platformer about a brave little chicken trying to reach the top. Jump, dodge obstacles, and be careful - one wrong move and you'll tumble all the way back down. Don't worry though - you can always climb back up, again and again...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359270/extras/c5f82137c44d0fd7a0d2418c8ac4970e.poster.avif?t=1767698714\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359270/extras/c5f82137c44d0fd7a0d2418c8ac4970e.webm?t=1767698714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359270/extras/c5f82137c44d0fd7a0d2418c8ac4970e.mp4?t=1767698714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br><strong>Every jump counts!</strong><br>Climb higher by chaining precise jumps. Miss a landing or hit an obstacle - you'll lose control and fall.<br><br><strong>Jump while in the air!</strong><br>You can jump even while airborne. Master your rhythm and momentum to stay in control and keep climbing.<br><br><strong>Avoid obstacles or fall!</strong><br>Hitting an obstacle stuns your chicken until you hit the ground again. Choose your jumps wisely!<br><br><strong>Prove your skill!</strong><br>Perfect the art of jumping, avoid every obstacle, reach the top, and become <i>The Bravest Chicken!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359270/extras/037c154ad4f870de64701cfbe1cba5c1.poster.avif?t=1767698714\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359270/extras/037c154ad4f870de64701cfbe1cba5c1.webm?t=1767698714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359270/extras/037c154ad4f870de64701cfbe1cba5c1.mp4?t=1767698714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Precise controls</strong> - simple to learn, hard to master. Every jump counts.<br></li><li> <strong>Single challenging level</strong> - one continuous climb from start to finish.<br></li><li> <strong>Hours of challenging gameplay</strong> - reaching the top usually takes 2-5 hours on your first try, but once mastered, it can be done in minutes.<br></li><li> <strong>A true test of patience and skill</strong> - inspired by games like <i>Jump King</i>, <i>Getting Over It</i>, and <i>Flappy Bird</i>.<br></li><li> <strong>Endless replayability</strong> - fall down, try again, and improve with every attempt.<br></li><li> <strong>27 achievements</strong> - can you beat the game in under 3 minutes or without hitting any obstacles? Well... you can try.<br></li><li> <strong>Simple yet charming visuals</strong> - a clean, minimalist style that keeps the focus on gameplay.</li></ul><br>Can <strong>you</strong> reach the top?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359270/extras/f23dfc900fd9506c8f4ee8c10feeefbd.poster.avif?t=1767698714\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359270/extras/f23dfc900fd9506c8f4ee8c10feeefbd.webm?t=1767698714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359270/extras/f23dfc900fd9506c8f4ee8c10feeefbd.mp4?t=1767698714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
